  "text": "Effects of RNAi and compound treatments on GFP reporters were assessed by fluorescence microscopy using a Nikon Eclipse Ti inverted microscope and CoolSNAP ES2 digital camera as previously described [CITATION_1] . GFP fluorescence intensity was quantified using ImageJ (Abramoff et al., 2004) . Statistical testing was performed using unpaired t-tests with the Prism6 software (Graphpad Software, La Jolla, CA, USA). A minimum of two trials with comparable results were performed for all imaging experiments.",
